Package easy.ease

Class EasyEase

java.lang.Object
easy.ease.EasyEase
public class EasyEase extends Object
EasyEase class provides an interface for easing motion using various algorithms. It encapsulates parameters and methods related to easing curve calculations and related functionalities.
